making a model
	declaring: CapitalizedName < ActiveRecord::Base
	attr_accessible: things we want to be able to change in a model object
	validations:
	has_secure_password <- function put in so that it does passwords lol

migrations
	new migration: in the same directory as your rails app, the following command: rails generate NameOfMigration
	then go to the new migrations file AppDirectory > db > migrate
	bundle exec rake db:migrate to run the migration